INSERT INTO `tour` VALUES (1,15,'2023-11-29 12:58:52.492741',2,'2023-12-25',4200,15,'Get to experience one of the unique cities of the southern India as you embark on a two days Kochi trip. As you land on the vibrant atmosphere of Cochin- also known as the Queen of Arabian Sea, our representatives will receive you with a grand welcome, and transfer you to the hotel. Before you plan the sightseeing of the city where history stands tall amongst the charismatic beauty of sea and the lush green surroundings, it’s recommended to unwind in a beautiful room there for a while.','Mesmerizing Getaway To Kochi','1701242932458-file.jpg',1,NULL),(2,3,'2023-11-29 13:07:53.953602',3,'2023-12-29',7000,16,'Rejuvenate yourself with this specially crafted 2 nights & 3 days Kerala Wayanad weekend holiday package to spend a refreshing break. Nestled in the Western Ghats, this little hill station is home to many gorgeous attractions.  This 3-day weekend tour package to Wayanad takes you to some of the most beautiful tourist attractions which will leave you in awe of the unbelievable environs as you embark on your weekend tour to Kerala. Explore the exotic wilderness of Muthanga Wildlife Sanctuary and the adventurous beauty of Soochippara and Meenmutty Waterfalls along with visiting the Chembra Peak and Banasura Sagar Dam, as part of your Kerala tourism package itinerary.','Kerala Wayanad Weekend Holiday','1701243473941-file.jpg',1,NULL),(3,18,'2023-11-29 13:18:09.773807',5,'2023-12-30',10000,20,'Designed exclusively for your loved ones, this best-selling 4 Nights, 5 Days Kerala houseboat & safari tour package lets you get away from the daily routine of your life. This vacation introduces you to the unparalleled fun that houseboats in Alleppey impart you. No wonder, with this vacation, you will also get an opportunity to enjoy a houseboat stay in Alleppey.','Kerala Houseboat & Jungle Safari  ','1701244089767-file.jpg',1,NULL),(4,20,'2023-11-29 13:55:41.719083',3,'2023-12-22',7000,20,'Kerala is calling you this vacation! Spend your time in Munnar this season. The town has been a major vacation destination and place of choice for many tourist. The scenic beauty of Munnar has made many days beautiful for its tourists.  It is a hill station, famous as a summer resort for the british during the British Raj. The town holds a blissful mix of nature and traditions. You will find a great countryside atmosphere within the town. Munnar has many places for your to offer to you. Eravikulam national park is one of the main tourist attraction, you will be visiting on this Munnar tour package.','A Blissful Tour In Munnar Package','1701246341709-file.jpg',1,NULL),(5,20,'2023-11-29 14:04:07.662483',4,'2024-01-04',8000,20,'Planning a weekend getaway in South India? Famous for backwaters, beaches, hill stations, and national parks, Kerala is one of the most visited states in India. The city of Kochi, also known as Cochin, is renowned for colonial heritage and a hub for Keralan arts. Located in the Western Ghats of Kerala, Munnar is popular for stunning viewpoints and verdant tea estates. Our 3 nights 4 days Kochi tour package allows travelers to explore the natural and cultural wealth of Kerala. The well-curated itinerary of our Kochi tour packages offers plenty of activities to enjoy such as boating, wildlife safaris, tea estate visits, and nature walks.','Charismatic Kochi Tour Package','1701246847648-file.jpg',1,NULL),(6,19,'2023-11-29 14:15:22.610434',4,'2024-02-20',10000,20,'A vacation in Kashmir Valley is a dream of many travellers. Starting from Srinagar, this 3 nights 4 days Kashmir tour package offers the best of Kashmir and its spectacular sceneries. It includes day tours to Gulmarg and Pahalgam from Srinagar and a number of fun activities for children and the adult members of the family. Choose the best of Kashmir tour package to treat yourself to the fresh air and the amazing weather of the Himalayas. ','Charismatic  Kashmir Tour Packages','1701247522604-file.jpg',2,NULL),(7,20,'2023-11-29 14:26:03.626827',5,'2024-02-25',15000,20,'Just the mention of Kashmir brings to mind images of the floating shikaras in Dal Lake, river valleys nestled amidst snow-clad mountains. With our Kashmir family tour itinerary for 5 days, you can witness all this and more. The trip begins with seeking blessings at the holy Vaishnodevi temple and concludes with a memorable stay in a houseboat.  Also included in the Kashmir family package itinerary for 5 days are sightseeing at Srinagar as well as visits to the stunning vistas of Gulmarg and Pahalgam. No words can do justice to the charms of this paradise on earth. Our Kashmir family tour itinerary for 5 days is the perfect way to experience the highlights of the region and come back with loads of memories.','Get the Splendour of Kashmir','1701248163613-file.jpg',2,NULL),(8,10,'2023-11-29 14:38:04.607157',8,'2024-01-20',30000,10,'Escape to the hills with Premium Kashmir Family Package that picks you from Katra, after you complete your Vaishno Devi trip. From Katra, proceeding to Srinagar, Sonamarg, Gulmarg, and Pahalgam, this 5 nights 6 days Kashmir package is apt for families looking for a summer getaway in the beautiful hills and valleys of Kashmir. It also offers a one-night stay in Srinagar houseboat.  Further, the Kashmir family package takes you on a joyful ride full of sightseeing tours to some of the most beautiful landscapes and valleys. It includes fun rides and activities such as the exciting Gondola rides in Gulmarg, white river rafting in Pahalgam, and the popular Shikara rides in Dal Lake. ','Premium Kashmir Family Package ','1701248884586-file.jpg',2,NULL),(9,15,'2023-11-29 14:47:20.057340',4,'2024-01-10',33000,15,'Relish a slice of heaven on earth where sprawling beaches are sprinkled with powdery white sand, and shores outlined by palm trees highlight the sapphire hued crystal clear waters. Choose from a plethora of Maldives family packages from Mumbai, Delhi, Chennai, and Bangalore and pick one that best suits your pocket and preferences. This well-designed package celebrates a great trip in one of the much esteemed resorts of Maldives – iCom Marina, Maafushi, where they are offered with everything that makes their trip of togetherness a true delight.','Ecstatic Maldives Family Package','1701249440051-file.jpg',3,NULL),(10,15,'2023-11-29 14:54:06.130077',6,'2024-01-20',40000,15,'Pump the brakes on your hectic lives for a little bit and head for a rejuvenating vacation with the Maldives family package itinerary for 6 days. With everyone’s lives getting so busy nowadays, it is important to take a break and head out for long, relaxing vacations like these together. Go lounge around on the beaches here, or play in the picture-perfect sea that encases this enchanting little island and grab a bite to eat while you watch the sun sink below the horizon as you have a chat and enjoy each other’s company.','The isle of Maldives & its coastal ','1701249846122-file.jpg',3,NULL),(11,15,'2023-11-29 15:02:08.578559',5,'2024-01-25',35000,15,'Delight in a vacation like never before with this 4 nights, 5 days Maldives family tour package. Experience the beauty of unspoilt beaches and crystal clear waters at the best as you set off for an unforgettable vacation at Eleven Trees Maldives, a tasteful resort in Maldives. Following your 5 days Maldives package plan, walk down the powdery sand beach, experience the waves gently kissing the shoreline, bask under the sun, and enjoy the intimate tropical atmosphere. Sink in the aura of Maldives, its culture, and beauty with this 5 days Maldives package from India and frame the most precious moments of a lifetime.','Refreshing Maldives Tour Packages ','1701250328567-file.jpg',3,NULL),(12,15,'2023-11-29 15:09:36.688332',4,'2024-01-19',25000,15,'Pattaya, a tropical beach destination located in Thailand is known for its pristine beaches, clear waters, buzzing nightlife, entertainment experiences, and a whole lot of food. The Pattaya 4 day 3 night honeymoon packages by TravelTriangle aims to provide the best of all these experiences combined into one itinerary. Enjoy the great entertainment experiences like Alcazar Show or get mesmerized by the reefs and other natural wonders at the Coral Island tour, there is a myriad of things to indulge in. The honeymooners are sure to spend a great time here because of the stunning locales, entertainment options, opulent accommodation options, bars, clubs, and amazing shopping opportunities.','Sensational Pattaya Tour Package','1701250776679-file.jpg',4,NULL),(13,15,'2023-11-29 15:15:09.980059',3,'2023-12-30',10000,15,'Renowned for its happening culture, seafood, magnificent architecture and nightlife, the capital of Thailand, Bangkok is one of the most popular honeymoon destinations on this earth. Book an enchanting tour of 2 nights and 3 days in Bangkok with us, and cherish your excursion to this Thai Metropolis with your beloved partner. Splendid temples, tropical climate, and royal palaces add a lot of glamour with an urban edge which is a treat for eyes. The city offers a myriad of experiences like wading through the floating markets on a boat and commuting on the tuk-tuks while exploring the city, which you might not get to do anywhere else. And, that’s the reason this city is also called as the ‘City of Angels’.','Way to Beguiling Bangkok Package','1701251109976-file.jpg',4,NULL),(14,20,'2023-11-29 15:29:50.695263',5,'2024-01-26',25000,20,'Bangkok and Krabi are two such destinations which enjoy a special place in Thailand tourism. Bangkok being the capital city of Thailand, is the treasure chest of the country and houses numerous tourist spots and is visited by vacationers throughout the year from all across the globe. People come here to let go off the stress and relax in the lap of nature. Therefore, booking a 4 nights 5 days Bangkok tour package seems the best way to avoid any last minute rush in deciding the itineraries.','Breathtaking Bangkok Tour Package','1701251990688-file.jpg',4,NULL),(18,5,'2023-12-24 18:38:22.906052',1,'2024-01-19',300,5,'Day 1 - Arrive in Cochin Upon arrival at the Cochin Airport, board the vehicle that will take you to your respective hotel. Cochin is a coastal city that lies on the western coast of Peninsular India. This port city enthrals travellers with its historical monuments, beaches and lush environs. Some of the major landmarks of this place are St. Francis Church, Mattancherry Palace and Santa Cruz Basilica.   After arrival at the hotel, check-in and take some rest. As the rest of the day is free for leisure activities, you may choose to savour the local cuisine, which is served at several food joints. Alternately, you can explore the bustling markets and streets of Cochin to shop for souvenirs. After a memorable day, return to the hotel for a comfortable overnight stay.','Intriguing Thekkady - Standard','1703423302836-file.jpg',1,NULL),(19,50,'2023-12-26 12:57:22.147300',2,'2024-01-01',2000,50,'Pure water','Soochipara waterfall','1703575642115-file.jpg',1,NULL);
